# Git commits

- Do not add `Co-authored-by`, `Made-with: Cursor`, or any Cursor attribution trailers to commits or PR descriptions.
- Use short commit messages when the user prefers that style (e.g. a single word or very short phrase like "bob" or "joe" when they ask for it).
